    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/1d2f49ac2f86274696782cec7b5761ad.webp?t=1770671254\" width=342 height=44 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hector Rodriguez is the bumbling scientist who, between making ends meet with odd jobs, has created the world’s first working time machine - the very invention that will one day destroy the world. At least, that’s what he’s told by the killers chasing him from the future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When a victim of his future legacy, Nyx, reaches back into 2032, it’s up to Hector to heed her warning and fix the disaster he’s destined to cause.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/61d30da5dab42a3549c0bef665bf1de2.webp?t=1770671254\" width=388 height=44 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the bustling crosswalks of Hong Kong to the cyberpunk back-alleys of Tokyo, you’ll explore sprawling cityscapes across futures as you seek to prevent an unfolding temporal catastrophe. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/56b503d5cb7be1d77ae067b1ada99485.poster.avif?t=1770671254\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/56b503d5cb7be1d77ae067b1ada99485.webm?t=1770671254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/56b503d5cb7be1d77ae067b1ada99485.mp4?t=1770671254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/96fa0b6374340fdcb12b13a143ceb975.webp?t=1770671254\" width=394 height=44 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a quest to unravel the truth, and leave the world as you know it behind. Experience time-bending triumphs, backstabbing betrayals, and all of the mysteries awaiting in-between. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/12031d67981e2ddfb5c087226a615754.poster.avif?t=1770671254\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/12031d67981e2ddfb5c087226a615754.webm?t=1770671254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/12031d67981e2ddfb5c087226a615754.mp4?t=1770671254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/d59486e5e77051376feef0563082887e.webp?t=1770671254\" width=312 height=44 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your wits to navigate a variety of challenges, from card games and street karaoke to cyber-hacking and android surgery. Push your luck, flex your skills, and do whatever it takes to elude the time-traveling assassins who are hot on your trail.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/b202212a07ed1569780ed5ba0a646bd6.poster.avif?t=1770671254\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/b202212a07ed1569780ed5ba0a646bd6.webm?t=1770671254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/b202212a07ed1569780ed5ba0a646bd6.mp4?t=1770671254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/61ed0b7349459eb44f386fc814f795b3.webp?t=1770671254\" width=501 height=44 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter a diverse cast of unique characters, each with their own opinions, desires, arcs, and flaws. Conquer the twists and turns of time paradoxes until you finally save those who are close to you and break the loop, once and for all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/22f0d8e9c174f31eeb48a4b9557abe05.poster.avif?t=1770671254\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/22f0d8e9c174f31eeb48a4b9557abe05.webm?t=1770671254\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188490/extras/22f0d8e9c174f31eeb48a4b9557abe05.mp4?t=1770671254\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
